Title: A storm of hearts
DateModified: '2019-02-19'
DatePublished: '2019-02-19'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/a-storm-of-hearts
SetInCountry: Australia
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Jake Wharton
AuthorCountry: United Kingdom (Great Britain
Text: A Young girl from poland is tired of her boring job and fake friends and decides
  she needs a trip around the world.  In Tailand she meets a guy called spencer whom
  is from canada and has her first romantic experience. She visits him over her life,
  but eventually comes to the uk. She is then suduced by a charming yet manipulative
  young man and cheats on her long-distance relationship. A love triangle between
  the girl and 2 handsome men from oposite sides of the world. A story that spans
  over years and decades and involves many differnt aspects and relationships that
  happen when you travel.
